dct_title_s: Barbaria Biledulgerid o: Libye et pars Nigritarum terra
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Probably issued in: Umbständliche und eigentliche Beschreibung von Africa ... / durch O. Dapper ... In Amsterdam : Bey Jacob von Meurs ... , 1670. Has watermarks. Includes ill. and decorative cartouche.
